="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-sm"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M12 4C10.8954 4 10 4.89543 10 6H14C14 4.89543 13.1046 4 12 4ZM8.53513 4C9.22675 2.8044 10.5194 2 12 2C13.4806 2 14.7733 2.8044 15.4649 4H17C18.6569 4 20 5.34315 20 7V19C20 20.6569 18.6569 22 17 22H7C5.34315 22 4 20.6569 4 19V7C4 5.34315 5.34315 4 7 4H8.53513ZM8 6H7C6.44772 6 6 6.44772 6 7V19C6 19.5523 6.44772 20 7 20H17C17.5523 20 18 19.5523 18 19V7C18 6.44772 17.5523 6 17 6H16C16 7.10457 15.1046 8 14 8H10C8.89543 8 8 7.10457 8 6Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Copy code</button></span></div><div class="p-4 overflow-y-auto"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">SELECT</span> 
    c.id <span class="hljs-keyword">AS</span> chat_id, 
    m.message, 
    m.timestamp, 
    l.Name <span class="hljs-keyword">AS</span> other_person_name, 
    l.Accounttype <span class="hljs-keyword">AS</span> other_person_type,
    <span class="hljs-keyword">CASE</span> 
        <span class="hljs-keyword">WHEN</span> l.Accounttype <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-string">'startup'</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">THEN</span> si.logo
        <span class="hljs-keyword">WHEN</span> l.Accounttype <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-string">'investor'</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">THEN</span> ii.image_path
    <span class="hljs-keyword">END</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">AS</span> profile_image_path
<span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> 
    chats c
<span class="hljs-keyword">INNER</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">JOIN</span> 
    messages m <span class="hljs-keyword">ON</span> c.id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> m.chat_id
<span class="hljs-keyword">INNER</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">JOIN</span> 
    chat_twopeople cp <span class="hljs-keyword">ON</span> c.id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> cp.chat_id
<span class="hljs-keyword">INNER</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">JOIN</span> 
    login l <span class="hljs-keyword">ON</span> l.id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">CASE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">WHEN</span> cp.person1_id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> :userId <span class="hljs-keyword">THEN</span> cp.person2_id <span class="hljs-keyword">ELSE</span> cp.person1_id <span class="hljs-keyword">END</span>)
<span class="hljs-keyword">LEFT</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">JOIN</span> 
    startups_information si <span class="hljs-keyword">ON</span> l.id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> si.startup_id
<span class="hljs-keyword">LEFT</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">JOIN</span> 
    information_investor ii <span class="hljs-keyword">ON</span> l.id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> ii.investor_id
<span class="hljs-keyword">WHERE</span> 
    cp.person1_id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> :userId <span class="hljs-keyword">OR</span> cp.person2_id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> :userId
<span class="hljs-keyword">GROUP</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">BY</span> 
    c.id
<span class="hljs-keyword">ORDER</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">BY</span> 
    m.timestamp <span class="hljs-keyword">DESC</span>;
</code></div></div></pre><h3>Notes:</h3><ol><li><p><strong>Image Path for Investors</strong>: Your <code>information_investor</code> table schema doesn't explicitly include an <code>image_path</code> or similar field for the profile image of investors. You might need to adjust the table or the query based on where you store investor images.</p></li><li><p><strong>Chat Participants</strong>: This query assumes chats are between two people as per <code>chat_twopeople</code>. Adjustments are needed if you want to incorporate group chats from <code>groupchat</code>.</p></li><li><p><strong>Timestamps</strong>: For converting timestamps into more readable formats like "today", "yesterday", or "x days ago", consider handling this within your PHP code using DateTime functions for flexibility and localization support.</p></li></ol><h3>PHP Code for Displaying Images</h3><p>Based on whether the chat participant is a startup or an investor, you can dynamically display the profile image using the fetched <code>profile_image_path</code>.</p><pre><div class="dark bg-gray-950 rounded-md"><div class="flex items-center relative text-token-text-secondary bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between rounded-t-md"><span>php</span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-sm"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M12 4C10.8954 4 10 4.89543 10 6H14C14 4.89543 13.1046 4 12 4ZM8.53513 4C9.22675 2.8044 10.5194 2 12 2C13.4806 2 14.7733 2.8044 15.4649 4H17C18.6569 4 20 5.34315 20 7V19C20 20.6569 18.6569 22 17 22H7C5.34315 22 4 20.6569 4 19V7C4 5.34315 5.34315 4 7 4H8.53513ZM8 6H7C6.44772 6 6 6.44772 6 7V19C6 19.5523 6.44772 20 7 20H17C17.5523 20 18 19.5523 18 19V7C18 6.44772 17.5523 6 17 6H16C16 7.10457 15.1046 8 14 8H10C8.89543 8 8 7.10457 8 6Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Copy code</button></span></div><div 