4 4.85067C23.0427 4.88379 22.937 4.94215 22.8668 4.98473L14.9024 9.58517C14.7025 9.69878 14.5366 9.86356 14.4215 10.0626C14.3065 10.2616 14.2466 10.4877 14.2479 10.7175L14.2424 21.9419ZM16.071 17.9991L20.4018 15.4978L24.7325 17.9975V22.9985L20.4018 25.4983L16.071 22.9985V17.9991Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></div></div></div></div><div class="relative flex w-full flex-col agent-turn"><div class="font-semibold select-none">ChatGPT</div><div class="flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex flex-grow flex-col max-w-full"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="eaa7df8c-6baf-4f82-89bb-7eb3595d0b5e" class="min-h-[20px] text-message flex flex-col items-start gap-3 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5 overflow-x-auto"><div class="markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"><p>With the updated database schema, the approach to fetching and displaying chats with the associated user images (whether they're a startup or an investor) remains essentially the same, but now we have a clearer path for the investor's image (<code>information_investor.image</code> is confirmed to store the image path).</p><p>Given this schema, let's outline the steps and SQL query adjustments needed to fetch the correct information for displaying chat lists with user images:</p><ol><li><p><strong>Joining Tables</strong>: Your query will need to join several tables: <code>chats</code>, <code>messages</code>, <code>chat_twopeople</code> (or <code>groupchat</code> if handling group chats), <code>login</code>, and conditionally either <code>startups_information</code> or <code>information_investor</code> based on the account type of the other user in the chat.</p></li><li><p><strong>Fetching the Latest Message</strong>: For each chat, you'll want to display the latest message, which involves a subquery to select the maximum timestamp per chat.</p></li><li><p><strong>Selecting the Correct Image Path</strong>: Use a CASE statement or conditional logic in your query to select the image path from either <code>startups_information.logo</code> or <code>information_investor.image</code> based on <code>login.Accounttype</code>.</p></li></ol><h3>Sample SQL Query</h3><p>Below is a sample SQL query that implements the logic described above. This example focuses on chats between two people:</p><pre><div class="dark bg-gray-950 rounded-md"><div class="flex items-center relative text-token-text-secondary bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between rounded-t-md"><span>sql</span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-sm"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M12 4C10.8954 4 10 4.89543 10 6H14C14 4.89543 13.1046 4 12 4ZM8.53513 4C9.22675 2.8044 10.5194 2 12 2C13.4806 2 14.7733 2.8044 15.4649 4H17C18.6569 4 20 5.34315 20 7V19C20 20.6569 18.6569 22 17 22H7C5.34315 22 4 20.6569 4 19V7C4 5.34315 5.34315 4 7 4H8.53513ZM8 6H7C6.44772 6 6 6.44772 6 7V19C6 19.5523 6.44772 20 7 20H17C17.5523 20 18 19.5523 18 19V7C18 6.44772 17.5523 6 17 6H16C16 7.10457 15.1046 8 14 8H10C8.89543 8 8 7.10457 8 6Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Copy code</button></span></div><div class="p-4 overflow-y-auto"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">SELECT</span> 
    c.id <span class="hljs-keyword">AS</span> chat_id, 
    m.message, 
    m.timestamp, 
    l.Name <span class="hljs-keyword">AS</span> other_person_name, 
    l.Accounttype <span class="hljs-keyword">AS</span> other_person_type,
    <span class="hljs-keyword">CASE</span> 
        <span class="hljs-keyword">WHEN</span> l.Accounttype <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-string">'startup'</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">THEN</span> si.logo
        <span class="hljs-keyword">WHEN</span> l.Accounttype <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-string">'investor'</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">THEN</span> ii.image
    <span class="hljs-keyword">END</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">AS</span> profile_image_path
<span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> 
    chats c
<span class="hljs-keyword">INNER</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">JOIN</span> 
    messages m <span class="hljs-keyword">ON</span> c.id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> m.chat_id
<span class="hljs-keyword">INNER</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">JOIN</span> 
    chat_twopeople cp <span class="hljs-keyword">ON</span> c.id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> cp.chat_id
<span class="hljs-keyword">INNER</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">JOIN</span> 
    login l <span class="hljs-keyword">ON</span> l.id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">CASE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">WHEN</span> cp.person1_id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> :userId <span class="hljs-keyword">THEN</span> cp.person2_id <span class="hljs-keyword">ELSE</span> cp.person1_id <span class="hljs-keyword">END</span>)
<span class="hljs-keyword">LEFT</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">JOIN</span> 
    startups_information si <span class="hljs-keyword">ON</span> l.id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> si.startup_id
<span class="hljs-keyword">LEFT</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">JOIN</span> 
    information_investor ii <span class="hljs-keyword">ON</span> l.id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> ii.investor_id
<span class="hljs-keyword">WHERE</span> 
    cp.person1_id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> :userId <span class="hljs-keyword">OR</span> cp.person2_id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> :userId
<span class="hljs-keyword">GROUP</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">BY</span> 
    c.id
<span class="hljs-keyword">ORDER</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">BY</span> 
    m.timestamp <span class="hljs-keyword">DESC</span>;
</code></div></div></pre><h3>Displaying the Chat List with Images</h3><p>The PHP code snippet for displaying each chat item remains similar to the previous example. Ensure to adjust the image rendering part based on whether the chat participant is a startup or an investor:</p><pre><div class="dark bg-gray-950 rounded-md"><div class="flex items-center relative text-token-text-secondary bg-token-main-surface-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between rounded-t-md"><span>php</span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-sm"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M12 4C10.8954 4 10 4.89543 10 6H14C14 4.89543 13.1046 4 12 4ZM8.53513 4C9.22675 2.8044 10.5194 2 12 2C13.4806 2 14.7733 2.8044 15.4649 4H17C18.6569 4 20 5.34315 20 7V19C20 20.6569 18.6569 22 17 22H7C5.34315 22 4 20.6569 4 19V7C4 5.34315 5.34315 4 7 4H8.53513ZM8 6H7C6.44772 6 6 6.44772 6 7V19C6 19.5523 6.44772 20 7 20H17C17.5523 20 18 19.5523 18 19V7C18 6.44772 17.5523 6 17 6H16C16 7.10457 15.1046 8 14 8H10C8.89543 8 8 7.10457 8 6Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Copy code</button></span></div><div class="p-4 overflow-y-auto"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-meta">&lt;?php</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">foreach</span> (<span class="hljs-variable">$chats</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$chat</span>): <span class="hljs-meta">?&gt;</span>
&lt;div <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span>="<span class="hljs-title">flex</span> <span class="hljs-title">items</span>-<span class="hljs-title">center</span> <span class="hljs-title">space</span>-<span class="hljs-title">x</span>-3 <span class="hljs-title">pb</span>-2"&gt;
    &lt;<span class="hljs-title">span</span> <span class="hljs-title">class</span>="<span class="hljs-title">relative</span> <span class="hljs-title">flex</span> <span class="hljs-title">h</span>-10 <span class="hljs-title">w</span>-10 <span class="hljs-title">shrink</span>-0 <span class="hljs-title">overflow</span>-<span class="hljs-title">hidden</span> <span class="hljs-title">rounded</span>-<span class="hljs-title">full</span>"&gt;
        &lt;?<span class="hljs-title">php</span> <span class="hljs-title">if</span> (!<span class="hljs-title">empty</span>($<span class="hljs-title">chat</span>['<span class="hljs-title">profile_image_path</span>'])): ?&gt;
            &lt;!-- <span class="hljs-title">Display</span> <span class="hljs-title">profile</span> <span class="hljs-title">image</span> <span class="hljs-title">if</span> <span class="hljs-title">available</span> --&gt;
            &lt;<span class="hljs-title">img</span> <span class="hljs-title">src</span>="&lt;?= <span class="hljs-title">htmlspecialchars</span>($<span class="hljs-title">chat</span>['<span class="hljs-title">profile_image_path</span>']) ?&gt;" <span class="hljs-title">alt</span>="<span class="hljs-title">Profile</span> <span class="hljs-title">Image</span>" <span class="hljs-title">class</span>="<span class="hljs-title">rounded</span>-<span class="hljs-title">full</span> <span class="hljs-title">object</span>-<span class="hljs-title">cover</span>"&gt;
        &lt;?<span class="hljs-title">php</span> <span class="hljs-title">else</span>: ?&gt;
            &lt;!-- <span class="hljs-title">Placeholder</span> <span class="hljs-title">if</span> <span class="hljs-title">no</span> <span class="hljs-title">image</span> <span class="hljs-title">is</span> <span class="hljs-title">available</span> --&gt;
            &lt;<span class="hljs-title">span</span> <span class="hljs-title">class</span>="<span class="hljs-title">flex</span> <span class="hljs-title">h</span>-<span class="hljs-title">full</span> <span class="hljs-title">w</span>-<span class="hljs-title">full</span> <span class="hljs-title">items</span>-<span class="hljs-title">center</span> <span class="hljs-title">justify</span>-<span class="hljs-title">center</span> <span class="hljs-title">rounded</span>-<span class="hljs-title">full</span> <span class="hljs-title">bg</span>-<span class="hljs-title">muted</span>"&gt;<span class="hljs-title">N</span>/<span class="hljs-title">A</span>&lt;/<span class="hljs-title">span</span>&gt;
        &lt;?<span class="hljs-title">php</span> <span class="hljs-title">endif</span>; ?&gt;
    &lt;/<span class="hljs-title">span</span>&gt;
    &lt;<span class="hljs-title">div</span> <span class="hljs-title">class</span>="<span class="hljs-title">flex</span>-1"&gt;
        &lt;<span class="hljs-title">p</span> <span class="hljs-title">class</span>="<span class="hljs-title">text</span>-<span class="hljs-title">sm</span> <span class="hljs-title">font</span>-<span class="hljs-title">semibold</span> <span class="hljs-title">text</span>-<span class="hljs-title">white</span>"&gt;&lt;?= <span class="hljs-title">htmlspecialchars</span>($<span class="hljs-title">chat</span>['<span class="hljs-title">other_person_name</span>']) ?&gt;&lt;/<span class="hljs-title">p</span>&gt;
        &lt;<span class="hljs-title">p</span> <span class="hljs-title">class</span>="<span class="hljs-title">text</span>-<span class="hljs-title">xs</span> <span class="hljs-title">text</span>-<span class="hljs-title">gray</span>-500 <span class="hljs-title">text</span>-<span class="hljs-title">white</span>"&gt;&lt;?= <span class="hljs-title">htmlspecialchars</span>($<span class="hljs-title">chat</span>['<span class="hljs-title">message</span>']) ?&gt;&lt;/<span class="hljs-title">p</span>&gt;
    &lt;/<span class="hljs-title">div</span>&gt;
    &lt;<span class="hljs-title">p</span> <span class="hljs-title">class</span>="<span class="hljs-title">text</span>-<span class="hljs-title">xs</span> <span class="hljs-title">text</span>-<span class="hljs-title">gray</span>-500 <span class="hljs-title">text</span>-<span class="hljs-title">white</span>"&gt;&lt;?= <span class="hljs-title">htmlspecialchars</span>($<span class="hljs-title">chat</span>['<span class="hljs-title">timestamp</span>']) ?&gt;&lt;/<span class="hljs-title">p</span>&gt;
&lt;/<span class="hljs-title">div</span>&gt;
