    <span class="hljs-keyword">FOREIGN</span> KEY (Investor_id) <span class="hljs-keyword">REFERENCES</span> information_investor(investor_id)
);
</code></div></div></pre><p>In this SQL statement:</p><ul><li>The <code>FOREIGN KEY (Startup_id) REFERENCES startups_information(startup_id)</code> line means that <code>Startup_id</code> in the <code>Swipe</code> table references the <code>startup_id</code> column in the <code>startups_information</code> table.</li><li>Similarly, the <code>FOREIGN KEY (Investor_id) REFERENCES information_investor(investor_id)</code> line indicates that <code>Investor_id</code> in the <code>Swipe</code> table references the <code>investor_id</code> column in the <code>information_investor</code> table.</li><li>The <code>UNIQUE(Startup_id, Investor_id)</code> constraint ensures that each pair of <code>Startup_id</code> and <code>Investor_id</code> is unique within the <code>Swipe</code> table, meaning a startup and an investor can have only one unique record regarding whether the swipe was successful or not.</li></ul><p>Please make sure that the <code>startups_information</code> table has a primary key column named <code>startup_id</code> and the <code>information_investor</code> table has a primary key column named <code>investor_id</code> for these foreign key constraints to work correctly.</p></div></div></div><div class="mt-1 flex justify-start gap-3 empty:hidden"><div class="text-gray-400 flex self-end lg:self-center justify-center lg:justify-start mt-0 -ml-1 h-7 visible"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-md p-1 text-xs text-token-text-tertiary hover:text-token-text-primary md:invisible md:group-hover:visible md:group-[.final-completion]:visible"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-md"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M12 4C10.8954 4 10 4.89543 10 6H14C14 4.89543 13.1046 4 12 4ZM8.53513 4C9.22675 2.8044 10.5194 2 12 2C13.4806 2 14.7733 2.8044 15.4649 4H17C18.6569 4 20 5.34315 20 7V19C20 20.6569 18.6569 22 17 22H7C5.34315 22 4 20.6569 4 19V7C4 5